Sorry for the 7 month wait on this port!
This map was made for CSGO, so if there are any issues with the port let me know!

A collab from down under with 8 mappers! bhop_oceanic
featuring - Lappyy, Buggajayjay, Maharero, biql, roger, masque, belä and FOOL! 

After a few months of work this map is finally done for all to play!

Special Thanks to
http://ausbhop.com/ and SlidyBat for providing servers for playtesting! 

The list of Credits is currently unfinished, so if you see one of your textures and/or models in this map and it isn't credited, please let me know and i'll add it to the list!
